// error-005-typed.scrml
// Error effect with typed errors. Tests: !{} with type patterns.

<div>
    !{
        | ::ValidationError err -> let msg = "Validation failed"
        | ::TimeoutError err -> let msg = "Request timed out"
        | _ err -> let msg = "Something went wrong"
    }
    <p>Typed error handler</>
</div>
